---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
    title="About Us | BrightMariner"
    description="Learn more about BrightMariner's mission to create the world's most comprehensive maritime knowledge base and exit exam preparation platform."
>
    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="relative pt-32 pb-48 overflow-hidden mesh-gradient">
        <div class="max-w-(--page-width) mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8 relative z-10 text-center">
            <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1 bg-canvas border border-hairline rounded-full mb-8">
                <span class="text-[10px] font-mono uppercase tracking-widest text-mute">Since 2021</span>
                <span class="text-xs font-medium text-ink">Empowering Future Mariners</span>
            </div>
            
            <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-semibold tracking-tighter text-ink mb-6 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
                Navigating the Future of Maritime Education.
            </h1>
            <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-body mb-10 max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
                BrightMariner is the world's fastest-growing maritime knowledge base, dedicated to helping seafarers master their profession and clear DG Shipping exit exams with confidence.
            </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 right-0 h-px bg-linear-to-r from-transparent via-hairline to-transparent"></div>
    </section>

    <!-- Mission Section -->
    <section class="py-24 bg-canvas">
        <div class="max-w-(--page-width) mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8">
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
                <div>
                    <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-ink mb-6">Our Mission & Vision</h2>
                    <div class="space-y-6 text-body text-lg leading-relaxed">
                        <p>
                            Started on March 3rd, 2021, BrightMariner began as an ambitious initiative to create a definitive, open-access repository for everything related to the maritime field. 
                        </p>
                        <p>
                            Our aim is to be the ultimate destination for maritime knowledge. Whether you are a student preparing for your first exam or a seasoned professional looking for detailed technical notes, BrightMariner is built for you.
                        </p>
                        <p>
                            We cover a vast collection of study materials across subjects like <strong>Marine Engineering, DNS, Navigation, Ship Stability, and Ship Operation Technology.</strong>
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
                    <div class="p-8 bg-canvas-soft border border-hairline rounded-2xl shadow-sm">
                        <div class="text-primary mb-4">
                            <svg class="w-8 h-8" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 6.253v13m0-13C10.832 5.477 9.246 5 7.5 5S4.168 5.477 3 6.253v13C4.168 18.477 5.754 18 7.5 18s3.332.477 4.5 1.253m0-13C13.168 5.477 14.754 5 16.5 5c1.747 0 3.332.477 4.5 1.253v13C19.832 18.477 18.247 18 16.5 18c-1.746 0-3.332.477-4.5 1.253" />
                            </svg>
                        </div>
                        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-ink mb-2">Detailed Notes</h3>
                        <p class="text-sm text-body">Comprehensive study materials for all major maritime disciplines.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="p-8 bg-canvas-soft border border-hairline rounded-2xl shadow-sm">
                        <div class="text-primary mb-4">
                            <svg class="w-8 h-8" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
                            </svg>
                        </div>
                        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-ink mb-2">Exam Preparation</h3>
                        <p class="text-sm text-body">Specialized tools and MCQs for DG Shipping STCW exit exams.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="p-8 bg-canvas-soft border border-hairline rounded-2xl shadow-sm">
                        <div class="text-primary mb-4">
                            <svg class="w-8 h-8" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 20h5v-2a3 3 0 00-5.356-1.857M17 20H7m10 0v-2c0-.656-.126-1.283-.356-1.857M7 20H2v-2a3 3 0 015.356-1.857M7 20v-2c0-.656.126-1.283.356-1.857m0 0a5.002 5.002 0 019.288 0M15 7a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zm6 3a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0zM7 10a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0z" />
                            </svg>
                        </div>
                        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-ink mb-2">Community Led</h3>
                        <p class="text-sm text-body">A team of enthusiast mariners giving back to the society.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="p-8 bg-canvas-soft border border-hairline rounded-2xl shadow-sm">
                        <div class="text-primary mb-4">
                            <svg class="w-8 h-8" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M21 12a9 9 0 01-9 9m9-9a9 9 0 00-9-9m9 9H3m9 9a9 9 0 01-9-9m9 9c1.657 0 3-4.03 3-9s-1.343-9-3-9m0 18c-1.657 0-3-4.03-3-9s1.343-9 3-9m-9 9a9 9 0 019-9" />
                            </svg>
                        </div>
                        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-ink mb-2">Global Access</h3>
                        <p class="text-sm text-body">Access your study materials anytime, anywhere in the world.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Founder Section -->
    <section class="py-24 bg-canvas-soft border-y border-hairline">
        <div class="max-w-(--page-width) mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-ink mb-12">The Founder</h2>
            <div class="max-w-xl mx-auto flex flex-col items-center gap-6">
                <div class="w-24 h-24 bg-primary rounded-full overflow-hidden border-4 border-white shadow-xl">
                    <img src="https://www.linkedin.com/in/azlanahmadsalmani/overlay/photo/" alt="Azlan Ahmad" class="w-full h-full object-cover" onerror="this.src='/favicon.svg'; this.style.padding='20px'"/>
                </div>
                <div class="space-y-2">
                    <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-ink">Azlan Ahmad</h3>
                    <p class="text-primary font-medium">Founder & Marine Engineer</p>
                </div>
                <p class="text-body leading-relaxed">
                    Azlan is a dedicated mariner who envisioned a world where high-quality maritime knowledge is freely available to everyone. Under his leadership, BrightMariner has grown from a simple idea into a platform that empowers thousands of seafarers.
                </p>
                <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/azlanahmadsalmani/" target="_blank" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-6 py-2 bg-white border border-hairline rounded-full hover:bg-canvas transition-colors shadow-sm">
                    <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-[#0077b5]" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M19 0h-14c-2.761 0-5 2.239-5 5v14c0 2.761 2.239 5 5 5h14c2.761 0 5-2.239 5-5v-14c0-2.761-2.239-5-5-5zm-11 19h-3v-11h3v11zm-1.5-12.268c-.966 0-1.75-.79-1.75-1.764s.784-1.764 1.75-1.764 1.75.79 1.75 1.764-.783 1.764-1.75 1.764zm13.5 12.268h-3v-5.604c0-3.368-4-3.113-4 0v5.604h-3v-11h3v1.765c1.396-2.586 7-2.777 7 2.476v6.759z"/></svg>
                    <span class="text-sm font-medium">Connect on LinkedIn</span>
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Final CTA -->
    <section class="py-24 bg-primary text-white overflow-hidden relative mesh-gradient-dark">
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 text-center relative z-10">
            <h2 class="text-4xl font-semibold tracking-tight mb-6">Join the Community</h2>
            <p class="text-xl text-white/80 mb-10 leading-relaxed">
                If you're passionate about maritime knowledge and want to contribute to our ecosystem, we welcome you to join our team of enthusiasts.
            </p>
            <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-4">
                <a href="/contact-us/" class="w-full sm:w-auto px-10 py-4 bg-white text-primary font-semibold rounded-full hover:bg-white/90 transition-all text-center">
                    Get in Touch
                </a>
                <a href="/mcq/" class="w-full sm:w-auto px-10 py-4 bg-primary border border-white/20 text-white font-semibold rounded-full hover:bg-white/10 transition-all text-center">
                    Start Learning
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
</Layout>
